aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cf45cf27ea46e5ddc7421ad8c63e145d771d03","tid":21952,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>窮撚未食過<br />\n大概咩價位?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間嘢sell高檔<br />\n食得飽你預$300一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食元氣板長都食300啦，仲要唔算大食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n元氣板長我一個人食200左右, 食過千兩唔就住叫400左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過真心好食過前面兩間"},{"pid":"fc699bf0457360e10f7f210eda8971731c093f7d","tid":21952,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做左會員，試過有次生日月去<br />\n折左都成千蚊埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過果次食左日本直送海膽、拖羅唔知幾多件、松葉蟹腳湯，差不多最貴都叫晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n元氣會員去千兩有冇優惠？？<br />\n<br />\n元氣越做越垃圾，家陣已經冇去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無"},{"pid":"cc083dcd71d704d1c92077b55a59ffa443bcc1ec","tid":21952,"uid":20248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間嘢sell高檔<br />\n食得飽你預$300一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食元氣板長都食300啦，仲要唔算大食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n元氣板長我一個人食200左右, 食過千兩唔就住叫400左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過真心好食過前面兩間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試完一次番唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d4eca9e32c3a52159b4c51e03252df86a64630","tid":21952,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"真係好食？以為係連鎖垃圾"},{"pid":"0e6c3687f7fdc618a04940449f1335fa129e727b","tid":21952,"uid":25618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好食？以為係連鎖垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連鎖之中算好好味 , 起碼你真係feel 到好味過元氣板長 , 貴左d錢都值 .. <br />\n<br />\n同埋水準都算穩定 , 我銅鑼灣番工成日食 , 唔會一次新鮮一次好伏咁囉 <br />\n<br />\n唔知地區關唔關事啦"},{"pid":"34f1d1c3291cd0ef607d051b8501ed254cde5693","tid":21952,"uid":8361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:31:32.000Z","msg":"唔係同元氣同公司架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得兩間用d野都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8d3b262f681f4ce21b1b9cf43d333d809892d2","tid":21952,"uid":25618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係同元氣同公司架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得兩間用d野都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係 , 但當同公司都有分別<br />\n<br />\n同料新唔新鮮都差好遠 , 上次屯門食元氣 , d刺身唔新鮮 , d飯又整到勁散 , 好難食 , 發誓唔再去<br />\n<br />\n我當d料同飯係一模一樣 , 淨係個手勢都差太遠<br />\n.所以我上邊先話可能關地區事"},{"pid":"4fa394f02cd3a161b5ec3c5d17b84a0c73c31dd3","tid":21952,"uid":39789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係同元氣同公司架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得兩間用d野都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係 , 但當同公司都有分別<br />\n<br />\n同料新唔新鮮都差好遠 , 上次屯門食元氣 , d刺身唔新鮮 , d飯又整到勁散 , 好難食 , 發誓唔再去<br />\n<br />\n我當d料同飯係一模一樣 , 淨係個手勢都差太遠<br />\n.所以我上邊先話可能關地區事</blockquote><br />\n上年summer做過千兩廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做幾個禮拜叫做廚房個個位都試過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n師傅(即係分店最高負責人 經理兼大廚)<br />\n話食材上千兩係高級過元氣<br />\n淨係壽司醋都用日本生產<br />\n佢言下之意應該想講元氣嘅壽司醋唔係日本野<br />\n其他分別就唔清楚 師傅冇詳細講"},{"pid":"974f0b3b873a5c37f10312f5d12905746a7793b0","tid":21952,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:01:52.000Z","msg":"咪又係美心"},{"pid":"a465f863651e7d0c86deafca9db8e51da8ddbbf7","tid":21952,"uid":63103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"千兩元氣都係垃圾美心開<br />\n呃我地香港人食黎食去都係佢啲野食<br />\n跟本同地產霸權無分別<br />\nstarbucks <br />\nsimply life <br />\nexp<br />\n通通都係佢<br />\n支持翻小店未仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363f58cdf7cc7b47804ea613e48d391345bbb593","tid":21952,"uid":56187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T22:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千兩元氣都係垃圾美心開<br />\n呃我地香港人食黎食去都係佢啲野食<br />\n跟本同地產霸權無分別<br />\nstarbucks <br />\nsimply life <br />\nexp<br />\n通通都係佢<br />\n支持翻小店未仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"9f11f97c9417438de9dad62fc7b73105b5e957ba","tid":21952,"uid":44080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好食過元氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyes"},{"pid":"5807487cb2a4c417456d2e19eccd4cf45c5c7e03","tid":21952,"uid":15883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:51:20.000Z","msg":"真心覺得係好過元氣好撚多，連鎖黎講佢已經算好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真係好撚貴，淨係食過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa6736bc3a1c97dd209936a39286e7d001f5e7f","tid":21952,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:13:54.000Z","msg":"貴元氣小小"},{"pid":"1598a4e84b05139704fa2735a7b0c91104e1334e","tid":21952,"uid":