心<br />\n好食咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認同，千兩算係咁，亦都係因為大集團，開飛機魚都會稍平過佢同級既刺身店，唔好盲反。你過到日本食番差唔多既野之前都唔見得會平到去邊，依家叫做匯水平有折扣。<br />\n不過千兩既熟食例如燒物等，一句講曬，求撚其其，未去到難食，但一定唔會再食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熟食果part真係十分同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔值佢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好一味齋屌連鎖 不如介紹番d有質素既細鋪<br />\n等多d人去幫襯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b72b42cbfb5e8e3475e072fa7b03af7dadc569","tid":21952,"uid":15939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"千兩算大型連鎖內最好食果幾間黎，佢啲質素的確唔差，唔係話打手唔打手，我又冇錢分又唔係做飲食，不過同元氣比真係差好撚遠。IFC 果間最正，我同幾個食開既都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb3b0ccb79bf25a68e8429bf11ea702ec42fd72","tid":21952,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用ae卡食都ok既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個刺身拼盤真係正又抵既<br />\n300幾 30塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6780c3015388f0c956098c70c120aa72ae96b8de","tid":21952,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"要食正既日本野梗係去日本食 點都一定隔離岩岩上岸就劏黎食最正"},{"pid":"82d951dfecce69e9b331d26e2ab34673de4f028d","tid":21952,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要食正既日本野梗係去日本食 點都一定隔離岩岩上岸就劏黎食最正</blockquote><br />\n鬼唔知咩，合唔合理先得架<br />\n食碗蟲草又飛去西藏，飲杯玫瑰茶又去保加利亞？<br />\n唔好咁離地啦。"},{"pid":"4dc5e2c1d29cb89f3fb099fb2b8b65c4cfd495b6","tid":21952,"uid":20248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><