ote><blockquote><br />\n下下用日本比就唔洗比啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本是但一間回轉師博手勢，好食過香港幾皮。<br />\n人地wasabi預先放左入飯面。調好晒味。<br />\n<br />\n香港d wasabi任加已經收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前去大阪同東京食過一間冇加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人乜柒都話要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你自己落wasabi好過"},{"pid":"20e93f17a7f3db739df1b5dc14cd0d123f7300b4","tid":21952,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而想問下有無巴絲會叫sake...我本身係酒鬼所以次次都會叫， 但從來未見過其他人會飲酒， 覺得自己好怪相</blockquote><br />\n有，出街食飯一定開酒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61780f49ebfa5b5072baffe1595cfa2215849817","tid":21952,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解你地覺得爭鮮難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得個價錢同味道算係咁<br />\n頹食俾元氣同爭鮮我揀，我揀爭鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你鐘意揀食垃圾無人會阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過口癮ok 不過二揀一都揀爭鮮就好被虐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實元氣魚尚爭鮮面頭塊野都係一樣用緊個D急凍貨<br />\n係舊飯既分別<br />\n元氣魚尚舊飯會酸度比較低<br />\n爭鮮舊飯仲低<br />\n不過爭鮮未食過堂食唔知佢乜料<br />\n<br />\n千兩酸度會接近返日本食到既<br />\n所以千兩都係嬴舊飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76973b4e5d8c94a0f7cefd46ea85baa566f676f","tid":21952,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔值個價"},{"pid":"afe5376cdf78299a71890806004bf9383c7e021e","tid":21952,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而想問下有無巴絲會叫sake...我本身係酒鬼所以次次都會叫， 